				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{P}}^ \ast ({\mathrm{P}}_{\mathrm{A}}^ + {\mathrm{P}}_{\mathrm{B}}^ - ) \to {\mathrm{P}}^ + {\mathrm{B}}_{\mathrm{A}}^ -$$\end{document}19. Subsequent theoretical models showed that coupling of these nuclear vibrational modes facilitates this process by removing the barrier for forming PA+PB-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
