For M3 (Fig. 3c), four components were extracted with time constants of 190 fs, 450 fs, 25 ps, and infinity. Component-1 represented P* and a minor population of B*. Component-2 contained the red shoulder of P GSB and thus was attributable to PA+PB-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
